# Hot-path profile — where the latency budget actually goes.
Output screencast/segment9-profile.mp4
Output screencast/segment9-profile.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1500
Set Height 620
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Padding 18
Set Framerate 12

Hide
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Type "# p95 is 1.42 ms. Where does that time actually go?" Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "bash scripts/demo_profile.sh" Enter
Sleep 12s
